content: Excellent game, can't wait for the next game, definitely recommend it !!
Great fun! Lots of puzzles that weren't too hard. Really enjoyed playing
Another great game from these folks. I've not found any other point-and-click developers who have been able to match or exceed their game quality.
Wonderful story puzzles very nice game. But your target 2 years one game release every year one game release try. Make the lost city 2

Excellent fire Maple game again. We love the graphics and illustrations and fun puzzles. Outstanding game, and we highly recommend. The plot is very intriguing and we were on the edge of our seats throughout the game. We have been playing these games for several years and continue to enjoy the high quality of the app developers of this company. Regarding the curse of the Cobra, we love the ending and have to say the bellhop is our favorite character.
Another great game from Fire Maple.
Thank you for another enjoyable game! Great graphics, challenging but not too difficult. I look forward to playing other games you create in the future.

Great puzzle game, just as the previous Fire Maple games were. There are no puzzles which are impossible to work out after a bit of thinking, and no objects in ridiculously hidden places. Thoroughly enjoyable.
Just as wonderful as ever! I beat it today and I just love how interesting every story line is!

Considerably easier than most FM games and maybe a bit shorter. Low tech graphics, but makes up for it in the wacky (but OS adventure game logical) charm of puzzles that fit together like a nesting doll. Even though I breezed through it, I'm satisfied with my purchase and hope they make more.
I greatly enjoy all of Fire Maple's games, and this game is no exception. Seriously check this and their other games out!
